年轻人。」 此外，李娟还辟谣了网络上对她「从小苦得不行」「天天捡垃圾」「挨继父家暴」的谣言，「这是根本没有的事。也不知道源头在哪儿。」李娟说她为此还曾尝试过投诉，但常常没有结果。她的朋友告诉她，在投诉的各种选项里，谣言举证是最难的。李娟用「一坨震惊」来形容她的感受：「我说我就是当事人，我自己站出来证明对方胡说八道难道也不行？」而朋友的一句话让她转变了对这件事的思考角度——「因为每个人都有说谎的权利。」与董宇辉对谈引热议，李娟发出「一坨声明」：感到咚大的一坨震惊 _ 直播 _ 朋友 _ 状态"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-981dd6707220e8411047702b7de65c80_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "59 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/665255329"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIho2ny9fz4tklEAMaCTExMDExMjA1NiDsxqu2BjAAOMQBQA5yCTY2NTI1NTMyOXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "15_1724674676.417393", "card_id": "Q_21001522", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 53}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "沙县馄饨里面的肉为什么是脆的？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "很脆, 很爽口, 一点都不会腻. 最近吃到一家店的饺子里面的肉馅也是脆的, 到底是怎么做到的?"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-4cdbe7a78385bec36e04c158655bedb7_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "57 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/21001522"}}, "attached_info": "CjwIho2ny9fz4tklEAMaBjU4MTA3MyDv/PmLBTAAOKgDQA9yCDIxMDAxNTIyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "16_1724674676.417627", "card_id": "Q_664974509", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 28}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "史湘云曾经也尽得贾母的疼爱，但后来贾母为何对她不太在意了？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-c0ae97699d944b301afb6c4dca53b060_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "56 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://ww